features.feature: 亲爱的用户，本次更新主要针对系统进行了优化，推荐您进行更新
• 新增密码解锁、控制中心等按压通透光感效果
• 新增排版助手功能，为您自动生成高质量版式
• 优化阅读助手使用体验，实现 YOYO 内沉浸式阅读
• 新增 PC 级 WPS office，轻松应对各种办公需求
• 新增 AI 帮记功能，会议场景下可托管听会并接收关键词内容提醒、智能生成会议纪要、实时语音转文本。体验路径：滑出侧边智慧多窗应用栏 > AI 帮记
• 新增字迹美化、智慧纠错、智慧联想功能，让批注更美观
• 优化通透模式显示效果
• 桌面场景下充电接入灵动胶囊，便于查看实时状态、快捷触达
• 提升系统稳定性，让您的平板运行更稳定
• 合入安卓 2025 年 10 月安全补丁，增强系统安全性。有关荣耀软件安全更新内容的信息，请访问荣耀官方网站 https://www.honor.com/cn/support/bulletin/2025/10

1. 新版本下载及安装过程会消耗部分电量及轻微发热，属于正常现象 2. 版本安装后重启期间会做部分系统优化，预计花费 1~3 分钟，请耐心等待 3. 升级完成后部分系统优化会在后台自动进行，系统会在后台自动优化，出现少量耗电，轻微发热是正常现象，1 天内即可恢复 4. 因部分第三方应用与 Android 16 不兼容，更新后可能会出现第三方应用无法正常使用的情况 (如闪退、卡顿、耗电等)。建议您在应用市场尝试将该应用更新至最新版本，若仍无法解决问题，请您耐心等待应用更新信息，并及时更新 5. 本次更新不会删除您的用户数据，但仍建议您在更新前做好数据备份 6. 如果您在使用过程中遇到任何问题，请访问“我的荣耀”应用或访问荣耀官方服务网站 https://www.honor.com/cn/contact-us 寻求支持
Dear user, this update mainly enhances the system performance. Update to enjoy the improvements
• A tactile light effect responds to your tap on the password unlock screen and in Control Center
• Formatting assist automatically generates high-quality layouts for you
• Enhances the Reading assistant to achieve immersive reading experience within YOYO
• PC-level WPS Office makes it easy to meet all your office needs

• AI Memo enables hosting in meetings and provides keyword reminders. It can also generate meeting minutes and convert speech to text in real time. Slide out the Multi-Window sidebar, then tap AI Memo to try it out
• AI correction, AI association, along with handwriting enhancement, make annotations more visually appealing
• Optimizes the display effect of Transparency mode
• Charging information on the home screen is integrated into Magic Capsule, allowing you to view real-time charging status and access it quickly
• Improves the system stability to make your tablet run more stably

• Android security patch (Oct 2025) has been incorporated for system security. For more information about Honor Security updates, please visit our website https://www.honor.com/global/support/bulletin/2025/10

1. The download and installation process of the new version will consume some battery power and cause slight heating, which is normal 2. During the restart after the installation, some system optimizations will be performed, expected to take 1~3 minutes. Please be patient 3. After the upgrade is completed, some system optimizations will automatically proceed in the background. During this period, the device may experience increased power consumption and slight heating, which is a normal phenomenon. It will return to its usual state within one day 4. Some third-party apps may not be compatible with Android 16 and may malfunction after the update (such as crash, lag, abnormal power consumption). Please update your apps to the latest version in App Market. If the problems persist, please wait for the upcoming app updates and update in a timely manner 5. This update will not affect your personal data, but it is recommended to back up your data before updating 6. If you encounter any issue during use, please get support by going to My Honor or visiting our website: https://www.honor.com/cn/contact-us
